OL,3,CGovernment plans new offence to crack
OL,4,Cdown on promoting Channel crossings
OL,5,Conline
OL,7,FThe offence would also outlaw the
OL,8,Fpromise of illegal working being
OL,9,Fpromoted online and could carry a
OL,10,Flarge fine.
OL,12,FIt comes as the Government grapples
OL,13,Fwith a record number of migrants
OL,14,Farriving in the UK after crossing the
OL,15,FEnglish Channel.
OL,17,FOn Wednesday, arrivals passed more
OL,18,Fthan 25,000 for the year so far, a
OL,19,Frecord for this point in the year.
