OL,3,CGovernment plans new offence to crack
OL,4,Cdown on promoting Channel crossings
OL,5,Conline
OL,7,FAssisting illegal immigration to the
OL,8,FUK is already a crime, but officials
OL,9,Fbelieve the changes will give more
OL,10,Fpowers to police and other agencies to
OL,11,Fdisrupt criminal gangs.
OL,13,FAccording to analysis by the Home
OL,14,FOffice, around 80% of migrants
OL,15,Farriving to the UK by small boat told
OL,16,Fofficials they used social media
OL,17,Fduring their journey, including to
OL,18,Fcontact agents linked to people
OL,19,Fsmuggling gangs.
