OL,3,CGovernment plans new offence to crack
OL,4,Cdown on promoting Channel crossings
OL,5,Conline
OL,7,FSpeaking on the announcement, Home
OL,8,FSecretary Yvette Cooper said: "Selling
OL,9,Fthe false promise of a safe journey to
OL,10,Fthe UK and a life in this country `
OL,11,Fwhether on or offline ` simply to make
OL,12,Fmoney, is nothing short of immoral.
OL,14,F"These criminals have no issue with
OL,15,Fleading migrants to life-threatening
OL,16,Fsituations using brazen tactics on
OL,17,Fsocial media. We are determined to do
OL,18,Feverything we can to stop them,
OL,19,Fwherever they operate."
