OL,3,CGovernment plans new offence to crack
OL,4,Cdown on promoting Channel crossings
OL,5,Conline
OL,7,F"Labour still has no clear plan to
OL,8,Fdeter illegal entry, no effective
OL,9,Fenforcement and no strategy to speed
OL,10,Fup removals. This is a panicked
OL,11,Fattempt to look tough after months of
OL,12,Fdoing nothing.
OL,14,F"The only clear and enforceable plan
OL,15,Fis the Conservative Deportation Bill,
OL,16,Fa no-nonsense strategy that allows us
OL,17,Fto detain illegal arrivals immediately
OL,18,Fand remove them without delay. The
OL,19,FBritish public deserve focused action,
OL,20,Fnot more of Labour's dithering."
